# Code Samples

## JavaScript

```javascript
function fibonacci(n) {
    if (n < 2) return n;
    return fibonacci(n - 1) + fibonacci(n - 2);
}
console.log(fibonacci(10));
```

## Python

```python
def fibonacci(n):
    if n < 2:
        return n
    return fibonacci(n - 1) + fibonacci(n - 2)

print(fibonacci(10))
```
